             was indicted for that <rs id="t18210214-93-off589" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210214-93-off589" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210214-93-off589" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               he, on the <rs id="t18210214-93-cd590" type="crimeDate">31st of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210214-93-off589 t18210214-93-cd590"></join>, 10 lbs. of lead, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210214-93-victim1000" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Scott
                        <interp inst="t18210214-93-victim1000" type="surname" value="Scott"></interp>
